game_description: ZOSU Zoo Demo - Demo of "ZOSU Zoo" - This is a relaxing and simple zoo experience with 40+ land animals to see, restricted access in the demo with a fence (can't see all animals in the demo due to the fence) - As a bonus, on mostly random spawners there are an additional 100+ sea creatures (they will not all be visible each play session), restricted access in the demo with a fence Gameplay: - In the demo there is a fence, the full game has no fence with full exploration available (can climb or jump over obstacles or into enclosures in full game) - Run and jump to find the eagles! (climb almost anything in full game)
